WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.470 --> 00:00:03.555
A diamond is forever. This tag along has

00:00:03.555 --> 00:00:06.480
appeared in every De Beers ad since 1948.

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:10.350
In 1999, two weeks before Mrs. Gerety died,

00:00:10.350 --> 00:00:13.110
Advertising Age named it the slogan of the century.

